seriesStmt.title: Gregor Joseph Werner: A thematic catalogue of his works

annot.p: Although this mass has also been attributed to Antonio Caldara (D-OB) and Marc'Antonio Ziani (A-HE), it is here considered as an authentic attribution as it is listed in Werner’s inventory of 1737/38.
da capo of the first 17 bars
trb 1/2 solo
vocal scoring (tutti vs solo) somewhat unclear
Et mortuos (Adagio, bars 37f) in common time
da capo of the respective movement in Sanctus
